  <thing id="arcElf" name="Elf" description="Whether tall or short, with pointy or really pointy ears, most elves are known for their grace, longevity, and connection to the natural world. This profile is based on that common conception of an elf, with high Agility (and an innate defense) but a lower wound threshold." compset="Archetype" uniqueness="unique">
