  <thing id="arcDwarf" name="Dwarf" description="The archetypal fantasy dwarf is tough, dour, eager to fight, and almost as eager to down inordinate quantities of ale. This profile presents just such a dwarf, with high wound and strain thresholds and, with a rank in Resilience, an ability to drink more than their share." compset="Archetype" uniqueness="unique">
