  <thing id="arcOrc" name="Orc" description="In many fantasy worlds, orcs are inherently evil or violent.\nBut PCs are known for defying expectation, and this profile could also easily represent a half-orc who lives among civilized society. Your setting may also have orcs who are not evil or violent by default, making this a reasonable character choice. As you might expect, this orc is strong and tough, but not the friendliest character." compset="Archetype" uniqueness="unique">
